<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>마이페이지</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.6/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

</head>
<body>

    <%- include('nav.ejs') %>
    
  <h1>마이페이지</h1>
  <p>안녕하세요 <strong><%= 유저.username %></strong> 님!</p>
  <p>이곳은 로그인한 사용자만 접근 가능합니다.</p>

  <div class="container mt-4" style="max-width:500px;">
    <h3 class="mb-3">비밀번호 변경</h3>
    <form action="/mypage/password" method="post">
      <div class="mb-3">
        <label for="pw" class="form-label">새 비밀번호</label>
        <input type="password" id="pw" name="password" class="form-control" required>
      </div>
      <div class="mb-3">
        <label for="pw2" class="form-label">비밀번호 확인</label>
        <input type="password" id="pw2" name="password2" class="form-control" required>
      </div>
      <button class="btn btn-primary">변경하기</button>
    </form>
  </div>
  
</body>
</html>


